[Episode 3]

4
00:01:13,470 --> 00:01:14,530
This formation...

5
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:16,410
Does it mean to kill?

6
00:01:44,710 --> 00:01:46,840
Why would the formation stop working?

7
00:01:56,020 --> 00:01:57,430
Oh no! I gotta run!

8
00:02:32,329 --> 00:02:34,200
You were using me to kill her

9
00:02:35,870 --> 00:02:37,930
so you could escape.

10
00:02:38,460 --> 00:02:39,610
How vicious.

11
00:02:41,750 --> 00:02:43,070
It hurts!

12
00:02:43,410 --> 00:02:44,220
Lord, please spare my life!

13
00:02:44,220 --> 00:02:45,750
Lord, please spare my life!

14
00:02:45,750 --> 00:02:47,270
T-There's another way

15
00:02:47,290 --> 00:02:48,560
to alter hosts

16
00:02:48,579 --> 00:02:49,760
without hurting others!

17
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,400
Say it.

18
00:02:50,650 --> 00:02:52,130
G-Go to the Filth Valley

19
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,110
and find my older brother.

20
00:02:53,110 --> 00:02:54,510
You have an older brother?

21
00:02:54,510 --> 00:02:55,200
Yes.

22
00:02:55,510 --> 00:02:56,950
There is something

23
00:02:56,970 --> 00:02:58,300
that people don't know.

24
00:02:58,670 --> 00:02:59,740
The Seven Sins Manual

25
00:02:59,740 --> 00:03:01,340
actually consists of twin Talisman Genies.

26
00:03:01,340 --> 00:03:02,590
The manual is made up of two parts.

27
00:03:02,590 --> 00:03:03,470
Only when they are combined

28
00:03:03,470 --> 00:03:04,170
can the effects

29
00:03:04,170 --> 00:03:06,150
of purging demon and punishing the sinful be achieved,

30
00:03:06,150 --> 00:03:07,070
But my brother and I

31
00:03:07,070 --> 00:03:08,400
split up long ago.

32
00:03:08,510 --> 00:03:09,630
I'm travelling around

33
00:03:09,630 --> 00:03:11,070
while he is guarding the Filth Valley.

34
00:03:11,070 --> 00:03:12,600
How dare you lie to me again.

35
00:03:13,270 --> 00:03:14,420
I'm not lying!

36
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:15,630
If you tame my brother

37
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:16,670
when the valley opens up this year,

38
00:03:16,670 --> 00:03:18,210
you'll get what you want!

39
00:03:18,670 --> 00:03:19,300
After all,

40
00:03:19,350 --> 00:03:21,230
comparing your and her qualifications to be hosts,

41
00:03:21,230 --> 00:03:23,320
your spiritual power is much stronger than hers.

42
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:25,320
I'm sure you can get me out of her body

43
00:03:25,430 --> 00:03:27,810
and help me and my brother reunite.

44
00:03:27,910 --> 00:03:29,510
If you dare to lie to me again,

45
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:33,000
I'll have you and your brother meet in hell.

46
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,770
If I lie to you again,

47
00:03:34,829 --> 00:03:36,670
let me be stuck here forever

48
00:03:36,740 --> 00:03:38,630
and never see the sun!

49
00:04:28,060 --> 00:04:29,110
Why am I here?

50
00:04:31,630 --> 00:04:33,390
Maybe you got too tired.

51
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:34,750
Just now,

52
00:04:35,510 --> 00:04:36,270
you fainted.

53
00:04:37,390 --> 00:04:38,510
I fainted?

54
00:04:48,310 --> 00:04:49,440
Regular pace.

55
00:04:50,630 --> 00:04:51,890
Not too light or heavy.

56
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:53,960
Not too slow or fast.

57
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,940
Not too strong or weak.

58
00:04:57,180 --> 00:04:58,640
I shouldn't have fainted.

59
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:03,830
Maybe I've been too tired lately.

60
00:05:04,470 --> 00:05:06,270
I'm busy trying medicine and cooking for you

61
00:05:06,270 --> 00:05:07,700
all day long.

62
00:05:08,130 --> 00:05:09,000
Listen,

63
00:05:09,150 --> 00:05:10,080
I especially

64
00:05:10,110 --> 00:05:11,300
made those three dishes for you

65
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:12,700
with the heart of a snake.

66
00:05:12,780 --> 00:05:14,330
If you are to repay my kindness,

67
00:05:14,330 --> 00:05:15,460
you'll eat them all.

68
00:05:15,550 --> 00:05:17,080
Do not leave a piece behind.

69
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:22,620
You made a tincture out of the snake's main body

70
00:05:22,620 --> 00:05:24,470
and three dishes out of its heart.

71
00:05:24,470 --> 00:05:26,260
You had it all planned out.

72
00:05:26,340 --> 00:05:28,270
Not a bit of the snake went to waste.

73
00:05:30,550 --> 00:05:31,470
Amateur,

74
00:05:31,670 --> 00:05:32,760
you don't get it, do you?

75
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:34,390
When I tried medicine on you previously,

76
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:36,060
I found you too weak to absorb nutrition,

77
00:05:36,060 --> 00:05:37,710
so I cooked that snake's heart for you

78
00:05:37,710 --> 00:05:39,040
to improve your health.

79
00:05:41,950 --> 00:05:42,750
What's wrong?

80
00:05:42,810 --> 00:05:44,140
Are you feeling unwell?

81
00:05:44,950 --> 00:05:46,070
Seeing how reluctant you were to take medicine,

82
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:47,070
I was infuriated.

83
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:49,390
Okay.

84
00:05:49,850 --> 00:05:50,990
I'll eat it later.

85
00:05:51,150 --> 00:05:52,070
You must eat it.

86
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:53,230
Otherwise, next time

87
00:05:53,230 --> 00:05:54,270
when I get angry,

88
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,909
I'll marinate a raw snake heart

89
00:05:55,909 --> 00:05:56,610
and put it in your mouth

90
00:05:56,610 --> 00:05:57,610
while you're ill.

91
00:05:59,909 --> 00:06:01,170
Nan Yan, come out here!

92
00:06:01,190 --> 00:06:01,720
Nan Yan,

93
00:06:01,750 --> 00:06:02,270
come out right away!

94
00:06:02,270 --> 00:06:02,740
You poisoner!

95
00:06:02,740 --> 00:06:03,930
Yeah, come out here right now!

96
00:06:03,930 --> 00:06:04,500
Come out!

97
00:06:04,590 --> 00:06:05,330
You stay put.

98
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:06,450
Don't go anywhere.

99
00:06:06,630 --> 00:06:07,470
Those are dangerous villains.

100
00:06:07,470 --> 00:06:09,200
Don't you cause me any trouble.

101
00:06:10,510 --> 00:06:11,100
I'm fine.

102
00:06:11,190 --> 00:06:11,990
You stay here.

103
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:19,910
Now that the Seven Sins Manual

104
00:06:19,910 --> 00:06:21,430
can't be acquired by force,

105
00:06:21,430 --> 00:06:22,890
I might as well hide in here

106
00:06:23,030 --> 00:06:24,070
to recuperate

107
00:06:24,470 --> 00:06:26,330
till the Filth Valley opens again

108
00:06:26,710 --> 00:06:28,970
for me to get the first half of the manual.

109
00:06:29,790 --> 00:06:30,790
Stop pretending!

110
00:06:30,950 --> 00:06:31,990
Come down here!

111
00:06:32,030 --> 00:06:32,560
Come out!

112
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:33,270
Come out!

113
00:06:33,710 --> 00:06:34,510
Keep yelling.

114
00:06:44,710 --> 00:06:45,920
What new stunts

115
00:06:45,950 --> 00:06:46,990
are you pulling today?

116
00:06:46,990 --> 00:06:47,290
We'll apologize.

117
00:06:47,290 --> 00:06:50,020
-Let's negotiate a truce.
-Fight me one-on-one.

118
00:06:52,409 --> 00:06:54,540
Come back when you reach an agreement.

119
00:06:54,860 --> 00:06:56,250
The chief told us to come

120
00:06:56,430 --> 00:06:57,630
and apologize to you.

121
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,320
I see.

122
00:07:00,860 --> 00:07:02,550
Today, you have no choice but to cave in.

123
00:07:02,550 --> 00:07:04,880
Tomorrow, you'll continue to provoke me.

124
00:07:05,790 --> 00:07:06,650
What about you?

125
00:07:09,750 --> 00:07:11,320
It takes two to create a conflict.

126
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:13,180
Look, let's both take a step back.

127
00:07:13,390 --> 00:07:15,510
From now on, we'll stay out of each other's business.

128
00:07:15,510 --> 00:07:16,510
What do you think?

129
00:07:17,590 --> 00:07:19,010
Now, it's your turn.

130
00:07:19,190 --> 00:07:20,470
What on earth do you want?

131
00:07:20,470 --> 00:07:21,230
Name a price.

132
00:07:21,430 --> 00:07:21,990
How many spirit stones do I have to pay

133
00:07:21,990 --> 00:07:24,110
in exchange for you leaving the Lunar Sect?

134
00:07:24,110 --> 00:07:25,110
Plus, your mother

135
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:27,230
must leave my dad as well.

136
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:30,290
Meng,

137
00:07:30,470 --> 00:07:31,630
is there some sort of misunderstanding

138
00:07:31,630 --> 00:07:33,030
between you and your dad?

139
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:35,420
Don't even try to sweet talk me.

140
00:07:35,710 --> 00:07:37,350
You don't want to leave, right?

141
00:07:37,350 --> 00:07:37,760
Fine.

142
00:07:37,990 --> 00:07:39,210
Keep your hands off of the poison

143
00:07:39,210 --> 00:07:40,670
and let's have a match using the magic tricks we know!

144
00:07:40,670 --> 00:07:41,200
Don't be afraid.

145
00:07:41,200 --> 00:07:42,030
Meng, fight her.

146
00:07:42,030 --> 00:07:42,470
Yeah.

147
00:07:47,590 --> 00:07:48,470
What's the matter?

148
00:07:48,470 --> 00:07:49,070
Yingying,

149
00:07:49,190 --> 00:07:50,390
what happened to you?

150
00:07:51,030 --> 00:07:51,830
I'm fine.

151
00:07:54,590 --> 00:07:55,420
Poisoner,

152
00:07:55,670 --> 00:07:57,070
did you poison her again?

153
00:07:57,370 --> 00:07:58,840
Give me the antidote.

154
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,860
I didn't get poisoned.

155
00:08:01,030 --> 00:08:02,690
I'm just feeling a bit unwell.

156
00:08:03,220 --> 00:08:04,350
Don't you touch her!

157
00:08:07,510 --> 00:08:08,710
S-S-She...

158
00:08:10,550 --> 00:08:11,670
Her spirit veins are blocked.

159
00:08:11,670 --> 00:08:13,340
Her aura and blood are stuck in the abdomen.

160
00:08:13,340 --> 00:08:14,990
She must have secretly practiced

161
00:08:14,990 --> 00:08:16,750
the pill-forming trick against the master's orders.

162
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:17,550
That's right.

163
00:08:17,750 --> 00:08:19,080
I poisoned her.

164
00:08:19,480 --> 00:08:21,490
There is no antidote to it.

165
00:08:21,800 --> 00:08:22,950
She must have figured out the truth.

166
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:24,310
Whenever she misbehaves,

167
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:25,390
the poison will kick in.

168
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:26,430
She'll be in enormous pain,

169
00:08:26,430 --> 00:08:27,830
and there won't be a cure.

170
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:29,900
Come on, sit down.

171
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,090
How dare you hurt Yingying!

172
00:08:33,090 --> 00:08:34,240
I'll make you pay!

173
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:44,210
Chubby!

174
00:08:45,750 --> 00:08:46,270
Come on.

175
00:08:49,590 --> 00:08:50,650
Take two pills now.

176
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:51,990
Then the pain will go away.

177
00:08:51,990 --> 00:08:53,630
She didn't reveal the truth.

178
00:08:53,830 --> 00:08:54,760
Why would she...

179
00:08:59,150 --> 00:08:59,830
I...

180
00:09:01,510 --> 00:09:02,710
If this happens again,

181
00:09:02,710 --> 00:09:04,710
you can ask me for medicine anytime.

182
00:09:06,060 --> 00:09:06,920
This is for you.

183
00:09:17,350 --> 00:09:18,950
Puppets for medicine tests.

184
00:09:19,130 --> 00:09:20,860
Although she is loud and noisy,

185
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:22,940
she does excel in practicing medicine

186
00:09:22,940 --> 00:09:24,210
and saving lives.

187
00:09:44,670 --> 00:09:45,800
This is more like it.

188
00:09:46,830 --> 00:09:48,560
Come on, let me feel your pulse.

189
00:09:55,830 --> 00:09:57,710
This snake heart can produce great medical effects.

190
00:09:57,710 --> 00:09:58,940
Right after I tried it,

191
00:09:58,940 --> 00:10:01,100
I could feel my aura and blood circulated better.

192
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:02,760
He has eaten a whole plate of it

193
00:10:02,940 --> 00:10:05,340
but his pulse feels the same as before. Why?

194
00:10:11,390 --> 00:10:12,530
Were you really

195
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:15,280
being a good boy when you waited for my return?

196
00:10:17,190 --> 00:10:18,830
You simply asked me to wait for you.

197
00:10:18,830 --> 00:10:20,690
You didn't tell me to be a good boy.

198
00:10:22,790 --> 00:10:23,270
What?

199
00:10:23,430 --> 00:10:24,390
Am I wrong?

200
00:10:28,150 --> 00:10:29,410
It doesn't matter now.

201
00:10:29,670 --> 00:10:30,430
If needed,

202
00:10:30,450 --> 00:10:32,510
I'll give you a larger dose next time.

203
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:03,470
Those who betray the Great Path

204
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:06,190
shall be held in the underwater prison of the Soul River.

205
00:11:06,190 --> 00:11:07,920
Even if they manage to escape,

206
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:10,150
they can never get rid

207
00:11:10,150 --> 00:11:11,810
of the smell of the Soul River.

208
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:13,600
So,

209
00:11:13,630 --> 00:11:14,830
no matter who they are

210
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:16,580
or where they are,

211
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:19,530
the Candlelight Beetles can locate them

212
00:11:20,070 --> 00:11:21,530
by following their smell.

213
00:11:30,690 --> 00:11:31,750
The northeast.

214
00:11:32,230 --> 00:11:32,750
Go!

215
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:40,390
Spiritual aura of five elements,

216
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:41,650
respond to my command.

217
00:11:42,430 --> 00:11:43,470
Fire, show up!

218
00:11:47,050 --> 00:11:48,550
Spiritual aura of five elements,

219
00:11:48,550 --> 00:11:49,810
respond to my command.

220
00:11:50,430 --> 00:11:51,230
Fire, show up!

221
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,870
Nothing happened.

222
00:12:01,870 --> 00:12:02,870
Where is the fire?

223
00:12:08,310 --> 00:12:09,560
Are you

224
00:12:09,870 --> 00:12:11,870
trying to start a fire to make pills?

225
00:12:14,610 --> 00:12:16,270
What do you know, amateur?

226
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:17,990
To make pills with fire,

227
00:12:17,990 --> 00:12:20,650
controlling flames is the most important part.

228
00:12:21,860 --> 00:12:23,340
There isn't any flame here.

229
00:12:23,340 --> 00:12:25,940
And you're talking about controlling flames?

230
00:12:26,430 --> 00:12:27,970
Easy for you to say.

231
00:12:28,270 --> 00:12:29,530
Do it if you know how to.

232
00:12:31,670 --> 00:12:32,870
Baffled, aren't you?

233
00:12:33,310 --> 00:12:34,390
Now, if you admit

234
00:12:34,510 --> 00:12:35,310
you're unable to do it,

235
00:12:35,310 --> 00:12:37,710
you can save yourself from embarrassment.

236
00:12:40,470 --> 00:12:41,360
So noisy.

237
00:12:43,100 --> 00:12:44,760
Do you even know how to do this?

238
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,690
I'd like to give it a try.

239
00:12:56,390 --> 00:12:57,130
Search carefully.

240
00:12:57,130 --> 00:12:58,270
If any situation comes up,

241
00:12:58,270 --> 00:12:59,600
report it immediately.

242
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:04,550
Go!

243
00:13:11,470 --> 00:13:13,600
Stop acting the hero if you can't do it.

244
00:13:13,860 --> 00:13:15,140
As a patient,

245
00:13:15,310 --> 00:13:17,320
you should stay relaxed.

246
00:13:20,350 --> 00:13:22,350
The fire's big enough, right?

247
00:13:24,470 --> 00:13:26,070
My heart-protecting pills!

248
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:27,230
You might get burned!

249
00:13:27,230 --> 00:13:28,190
If you don't want to help,

250
00:13:28,190 --> 00:13:29,200
just back off.

251
00:13:29,230 --> 00:13:30,150
Why do you have to stir up trouble?

252
00:13:30,150 --> 00:13:30,960
My mom has to take this medicine

253
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:32,110
on time every month.

254
00:13:32,190 --> 00:13:33,390
It allows of no delay!

255
00:13:33,870 --> 00:13:34,470
Watch out!

256
00:13:47,850 --> 00:13:49,110
Silver mermaid pearl?

257
00:13:49,820 --> 00:13:51,280
What is her real identity?

258
00:13:52,030 --> 00:13:53,350
Why does she have the devil-repelling

259
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:54,950
treasure of the spirit clan?

260
00:14:03,970 --> 00:14:05,030
What are you doing?

261
00:14:11,270 --> 00:14:13,390
Fortunately, the fire died out quickly.

262
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:14,120
Don't worry.

263
00:14:14,150 --> 00:14:15,210
The pills are fine.

264
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:18,070
Practicing medicine and cooking pills require great caution.

265
00:14:18,070 --> 00:14:18,750
Besides,

266
00:14:18,770 --> 00:14:19,630
in the furnace,

267
00:14:19,670 --> 00:14:21,270
there are the precious heart-protecting pills.

268
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:22,380
Two pills in total.

269
00:14:22,590 --> 00:14:23,770
One is for my mom,

270
00:14:23,790 --> 00:14:25,120
and the other is for you.

271
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:35,710
Elder,

272
00:14:36,010 --> 00:14:37,830
the Candlelight Beetles reacted as usual.

273
00:14:37,830 --> 00:14:38,900
I'm afraid

274
00:14:39,580 --> 00:14:40,260
there aren't traces of Shao Cang

275
00:14:40,260 --> 00:14:41,270
in the Lunar Sect.

276
00:14:48,590 --> 00:14:49,450
All disciples,

277
00:14:49,470 --> 00:14:51,000
assemble in the square now!

278
00:14:53,070 --> 00:14:54,430
What happened?

279
00:14:56,710 --> 00:14:57,670
Stop staring at it.

280
00:14:57,670 --> 00:14:59,200
It's none of your business.

281
00:14:59,230 --> 00:14:59,960
Come with me.

282
00:15:05,950 --> 00:15:06,680
Get in there.

283
00:15:08,110 --> 00:15:09,550
What do you want this time?

284
00:15:09,550 --> 00:15:10,710
To cure your heart disease,

285
00:15:10,710 --> 00:15:11,960
pills aren't enough.

286
00:15:12,110 --> 00:15:14,190
Acupuncture, medicinal cuisine, and herbal steam baths

287
00:15:14,190 --> 00:15:15,150
are all essential.

288
00:15:15,150 --> 00:15:15,950
Just hop in it.

289
00:15:17,270 --> 00:15:18,670
This is unnecessary, is it?

290
00:15:18,670 --> 00:15:19,890
Unnecessary?

