876
00:40:45,790 --> 00:40:47,650
since it's a life-and-death vow,

877
00:40:47,790 --> 00:40:49,120
you can't go against it.

878
00:40:49,950 --> 00:40:51,440
If you and Yan are

879
00:40:51,470 --> 00:40:52,950
ten miles apart in the future,

880
00:40:52,950 --> 00:40:53,830
you will

881
00:40:54,670 --> 00:40:56,270
die of an explosion.

882
00:41:00,350 --> 00:41:01,440
Just kidding.

883
00:41:02,030 --> 00:41:04,190
The Seal of Romance will bring you romance when you fall in love

884
00:41:04,190 --> 00:41:06,720
and erase all your memories when you break up.

885
00:41:06,830 --> 00:41:08,070
You'll see for yourselves

886
00:41:08,070 --> 00:41:09,350
exactly how it feels.

887
00:41:09,670 --> 00:41:10,920
The moon is high in the sky.

888
00:41:10,920 --> 00:41:11,910
The God of Wealth is blessing me.

889
00:41:11,910 --> 00:41:13,890
I'm going to make a fortune!

890
00:41:14,990 --> 00:41:16,190
Remember what I said.

891
00:41:16,830 --> 00:41:18,660
Take good care of Yan.

892
00:41:32,670 --> 00:41:34,150
Chief Nan Fang intended to entrust Nan Yan

893
00:41:34,150 --> 00:41:35,070
to me.

894
00:41:36,830 --> 00:41:37,870
This is strange.

895
00:41:38,620 --> 00:41:40,300
How many times have I told you?

896
00:41:40,390 --> 00:41:42,230
You have heart disease. You can't drink.

897
00:41:42,230 --> 00:41:43,790
I just took a sip.

898
00:41:44,390 --> 00:41:45,310
I can't

899
00:41:46,630 --> 00:41:48,270
stay with you forever.

900
00:41:51,350 --> 00:41:52,150
Could it be...

901
00:41:53,310 --> 00:41:55,970
Chief Nan Fang knew her hour of death was coming?

902
00:41:57,710 --> 00:42:00,080
Yan knows nothing about

903
00:42:00,310 --> 00:42:01,640
my identity and my past.

904
00:42:01,830 --> 00:42:03,350
Don't mention it to her.

905
00:42:03,710 --> 00:42:04,990
The less she knows,

906
00:42:05,150 --> 00:42:06,350
the safer she will be.

907
00:42:19,310 --> 00:42:20,750
It seems that Chief Nan Fang doesn't know that

908
00:42:20,750 --> 00:42:21,920
the second half of the Talisman Genie

909
00:42:21,920 --> 00:42:23,070
is on Nan Yan.

910
00:42:23,590 --> 00:42:24,150
Fine.

911
00:42:24,670 --> 00:42:26,070
I'll protect her for now.

912
00:42:26,510 --> 00:42:27,550
After I get the whole Talisman Genie,

913
00:42:27,550 --> 00:42:28,470
I'll leave.

914
00:43:00,270 --> 00:43:01,400
Where have you been?

915
00:43:01,950 --> 00:43:02,950
I just took a walk.

916
00:43:02,950 --> 00:43:03,830
Took a walk?

917
00:43:04,790 --> 00:43:06,990
Aren't you afraid of being discovered?

918
00:43:08,710 --> 00:43:09,570
Discover what?

919
00:43:11,590 --> 00:43:12,510
I mean

920
00:43:14,310 --> 00:43:15,840
you were in

921
00:43:15,870 --> 00:43:16,950
the Solar Sect in Xichuan.

922
00:43:16,950 --> 00:43:18,880
But you suddenly came to the North.

923
00:43:19,020 --> 00:43:19,990
Did you...

924
00:43:21,470 --> 00:43:22,430
Did you make huge mistakes

925
00:43:22,430 --> 00:43:23,220
before?

926
00:43:23,910 --> 00:43:24,830
I'm now hiding you

927
00:43:24,830 --> 00:43:25,940
in the sect.

928
00:43:26,270 --> 00:43:27,870
If someone sees you,

929
00:43:27,990 --> 00:43:29,790
I can't explain clearly to them.

930
00:43:30,950 --> 00:43:32,480
Even if something really happened

931
00:43:32,480 --> 00:43:33,150
in the Solar Sect

932
00:43:33,150 --> 00:43:34,680
that involved human lives,

933
00:43:35,070 --> 00:43:36,490
you're a kind doctor,

934
00:43:36,550 --> 00:43:37,660
I guess

935
00:43:37,790 --> 00:43:39,520
you won't turn away a dying man.

936
00:43:55,110 --> 00:43:56,110
Let me take a look.

937
00:44:09,910 --> 00:44:11,040
Why are you sighing?

938
00:44:12,190 --> 00:44:13,590
Forgive my incompetence.

939
00:44:13,590 --> 00:44:15,120
Although I'm a kind doctor,

940
00:44:15,190 --> 00:44:17,250
I've used all my knowledge.

941
00:44:17,350 --> 00:44:18,390
Your heart disease

942
00:44:18,390 --> 00:44:19,650
is not getting better,

943
00:44:19,750 --> 00:44:21,000
but even worse.

944
00:44:23,360 --> 00:44:24,820
You were so confident back then

945
00:44:24,820 --> 00:44:25,750
that I thought

946
00:44:25,960 --> 00:44:27,510
you were the only one in my life.

947
00:44:27,510 --> 00:44:28,710
Now it's only been two days,

948
00:44:28,710 --> 00:44:30,170
and you're abandoning me?

949
00:44:30,710 --> 00:44:31,640
Miss,

950
00:44:31,670 --> 00:44:32,870
is it a bit hasty?

951
00:44:34,670 --> 00:44:35,410
Previously,

952
00:44:35,440 --> 00:44:37,190
I was just bluffing

953
00:44:37,350 --> 00:44:38,670
to fool you

954
00:44:38,830 --> 00:44:39,830
to stay.

955
00:44:41,680 --> 00:44:43,110
If I leave now,

956
00:44:43,350 --> 00:44:44,350
you have no one to test the medicine anymore,

957
00:44:44,350 --> 00:44:46,610
what about your mother's heart disease?

958
00:44:47,190 --> 00:44:47,790
My mother?

959
00:44:49,200 --> 00:44:49,990
My mother?

960
00:44:50,890 --> 00:44:52,550
God bless her.

961
00:44:52,630 --> 00:44:54,220
Don't worry too much.

962
00:44:54,310 --> 00:44:56,030
Now, the most important thing to you

963
00:44:56,030 --> 00:44:56,830
is to save your life.

964
00:44:56,830 --> 00:44:58,240
Don't waste time

965
00:44:58,310 --> 00:44:59,230
because of me.

966
00:45:00,950 --> 00:45:01,810
Come on. Go now.

967
00:45:03,910 --> 00:45:05,190
But I believe in fate

968
00:45:05,510 --> 00:45:07,150
the most.

969
00:45:07,840 --> 00:45:08,830
Since God arranged for us

970
00:45:08,830 --> 00:45:09,890
to meet each other,

971
00:45:10,070 --> 00:45:12,230
no matter how many good doctors in other places,

972
00:45:12,230 --> 00:45:13,550
I only trust you.

973
00:45:15,910 --> 00:45:17,870
Your life is more important than the fate!

974
00:45:17,870 --> 00:45:19,450
If anything happens to you,

975
00:45:19,490 --> 00:45:20,890
I'll blame myself for it.

976
00:45:21,350 --> 00:45:22,810
No need to be modest, miss.

977
00:45:27,230 --> 00:45:29,230
It's my fault that I took in this man.

978
00:45:29,230 --> 00:45:31,110
I invited my own trouble.

979
00:45:31,910 --> 00:45:34,230
The Seal of Romance actually has an upside.

980
00:45:34,230 --> 00:45:35,890
It enables me to read her mind.

981
00:45:36,980 --> 00:45:38,800
Can she read mine as well?

982
00:45:39,670 --> 00:45:41,110
Why is he so quiet?

983
00:45:42,550 --> 00:45:43,790
Has he found out

984
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:45,930
I've realized that he's Shao Cang?

985
00:45:46,790 --> 00:45:47,870
It seems like she can't

986
00:45:47,870 --> 00:45:48,710
read my mind.

987
00:45:49,310 --> 00:45:50,370
That's good for me.

988
00:45:51,540 --> 00:45:52,620
Don't panic.

989
00:45:52,950 --> 00:45:53,550
Oh, right.

990
00:45:53,590 --> 00:45:55,320
I heard from Mu Zhanting

991
00:45:55,430 --> 00:45:56,590
that the Dragon Capital of the East Sea

992
00:45:56,590 --> 00:45:57,670
has many highly skilled doctors.

993
00:45:57,670 --> 00:45:58,110
You can go there and...

994
00:45:58,110 --> 00:45:59,440
I'm not going anywhere.

995
00:46:03,590 --> 00:46:05,390
You should stay in the Lunar Sect

996
00:46:05,790 --> 00:46:07,390
and treat me without worries

997
00:46:09,150 --> 00:46:09,800
till

998
00:46:13,180 --> 00:46:14,890
the Five-Poison Heart Pills are ready.
